title: Biden administration urged Zelensky not to leave Ukraine and visit Munich - CNN

description: Biden administration officials have privately urged Ukrainian President Volodymyr Zelensky not to leave Ukraine and visit Munich on Saturday given concerns about a possible incursion from Russia, according to three US officials and one senior Ukrainian official.
